Name

The name was first revealed in the PS3 port of the pachinko game CR Neon Genesis Evangelion 7: The Pulse of Life.Min nano EVA FAN. "Eva Mark.06's Spear appears to be called the Spear of Cassius!" Retrieved 2013/05/10. 

"Cassius" appears to derive from "Gaius Cassius Longinus," a name for the soldier who pierced Jesus' side that was established by the Greek patriarch Germanus in 715 AD.<ref>2005. Smith, Jerry E., and George Piccard. Secret of the Holy Lance: The Spear of Destiny in History and Legend. Adventures Unlimited Press, Kempton (Illino
